social_posts.post_text: Happy Birthday Nan!!!!! @sav.annahccox The last 14 years have flown by and no matter how little we sleep to savor every second of every day there seems to be nothing we can do to slow time down. I’m so thankful that your willing to fly all over the country just to ride in the truck with me for hours and hours to the next tournament. The older you get I worry less and less cause I know you’ll be able to make it in life just fine. Thank you for sticking with me through rough times even if it was court ordered. Love you so much Nan! Happy Birthday!

I’m About 5 days late but happy 20th birthday to my boy @adamparkerrrrrr aka @nothingnormal8 6 years ago I took u Okeechobee for a full 14 hour day of pre practice. It’s been nothing but fake smiles fishin from that day on.lol Love you bud glad we got to spend the day together.
We got a couple nibbles today. Congrats to @gunnarstanton and his dad  @zolafspeaks for catching there PB within a min of each other. @jonnybclear tomorrow is your turn.
Caught some nice ones with @gunnarstanton and @jonnybclear the last two days. If your coming to Florida u might want to pick up some @berkleyfishing #crashcraw from @tacklewarehouse
What a deck! @crestlinerboats got it going on. Another big that fell for the crash craw. I would never boat flip a fish that size but @robmatsuura made me.
The fishing trips from the @bassfishinghof auction have been a blast! Had another big flipping the crash craw and the boys Tom and @cjennings27 caught more then we could keep track of.
Last day of @bassfishinghof auction trip with Tom and @cjennings27 . With temps dropping they got in the thick stuff! Ordered 20 more packs of crash craws from @tacklewarehouse midday 😂
Breaking in the new Crestliner
Hope this is how the 2023 season is going to go! @mikeiaconelli designed @berkleyfishing Gilly…. Should of threw it more last year
This lake is where my dreams became a reality 13 years ago. Tomorrow kicks off the @bass_nation elites season on #lakeokeechobee
May of lost $100 to @sethfeiderfishing for catching over 15 pounds but we’re in 25th place going Into day 2 of @bass_nation #elites
Just barely made the @bass_nation #elite Saturday cut! Going to need 5 bites like this if where going to even have a chance of making the top 10.
Lil got second in the TSA today with captain @keith_carsonn then proceeded to have a photo shoot on the @mlfbig5official stage 🤦🏻‍♂️
Stop #2 of the @bass_nation Elites. This lake has whooped up on me time again and again…… tomorrow it’s my turn  boat #94 5:00 check in see you guys at  weigh ins
No idea how we recovered today but it was magical and we’re sitting in 11th going into day2.
Back on @bass_nation live for day 3 of lake Seminole. In 8th I think the lake is fixing to turn on. Let’s make that cut.
Just missed the top 10 cut at Seminole which is going to let us catch the last day of practice for the @mlfbig5official on Clark’s Hill this week.

13 years ago @keith_carsonn and I were so broke and didn’t have enough money to even make it home from the tournament. Some how we won the @fomntt regional and national points on Clark’s Hill. That’s when we put all the money from that tournament and joined the FLW Tour now @mlfbig5official . This lake has always held a special place in my heart all these years and tomorrow the Dream is a reality we get to compete in the MLF invitational. See u guys on MLF live tomorrow. Boat# 147 @alodomfomnttcom
Sitting in 19th going into day2. Won’t have the @mlfbig5official live camera tomorrow but @keith_carsonn will!

In 10th going Into the final day of @mlfbig5official on Clark’s Hill. This lake is so much fun to fish and the the people that live around here are great. Besides the one that told @tomredington he was #1 lol hope the town will have us back soon.
How I feel watching @majorleaguefishingofficial RedCrest while I’m home not fishing in it….. @robmatsuura can I get my @berkleyfishing #canewalker back?
Boat #19 tomorrow in my first ever @thenationalpfl I’ll have to say when u find a bass at Pickwick they eat it.
Tomorrow kicks off Day 1 of the Bassmaster classic. You practice your whole life for this tournament. Let’s see if it pays off this week. See u guys on live
We got us 5 keepers today! In 4th place going into day2 of the Bassmaster Classic! Let’s get 5 more tomorrow
In 2nd going Into the final day of the Bassmaster Classic!

April Fools prank with @johncox_fishing explained. Some of u sniffed it out. Hopefully those who played along got a smile from it. John n I certainly had fun with it. And yes, that is is Fanta Zero n Sprite Zero in my back seat #balleralert

Let’s take a look back and review the @bassproshops Top Lures segment during the 2023 Bassmaster Classic! @johncox_fishing relied on a Berkley Frittside to secure another Top 5 finish on the Tennessee River fishery known as Fort Loudoun and Tellico. 

Watch Cox compete at Lake Murray, South Carolina for the upcoming Elite Series tournament from April 20th - 23rd! 

#Bassmaster #BassmasterClassic #BassElite

Back at it again this week on lake Eufaula Oklahoma for the @mlfbig5official invitational. This place is really unknown for most of the field. It seems to fish small but Deff has some bass, how many? idk, We’ll find out tomorrow when day 1 kicks off.
Just outside the top 50 going Into day 2 of the @mlfbig5official invitationals on lake Eufaula. Thanks for the pics @pleeth and @robmatsuura
Made a big jump to 17th place going into the final day of the @mlfbig5official invitational. I’m starting to like lake Eufaula Oklahoma! Thanks for the crispy pic @pleeth

Got to thank the wife for flying out to Oklahoma then Uberin for 3 hrs to weighins to drive threw the night and morning for 15 hours to jump back on plane that would be delayed for half the day. Just to get me to Lake murry for day 1 of practice.  Thanks Babe !!!
Stop number 3 for the @bass_nation Elite on Lake Murray and stop #7 for me this week. This one is going to be a lot of fun. Photo credit @jonaaseng
In 30th after day one. Got to make some ground up tomorrow and make the 50 cut!
Jumped to 10th place in the @bass_nation elite on lake Murray. Let make the top ten cut tomorrow! See u guys on live

@johncox_fishing catches an unexpected 5️⃣ pound biggun!! Find out who will return for Championship Sunday TODAY at 3:00 PM ET on Bassmaster.com! 
#Bassmaster #BassElite #LakeMurray
In 5th going into the final day of the @bass_nation elite on lake Murray. 4 pounds off the lead! This place is really special. Can’t wait to see how it plays out tomorrow

Cox catches a flurry on Lake Murray‼️ @johncox_fishing is one of the most enjoyable anglers to watch - his enthusiasm on the water is contagious! 

Will Cox take the lead? Find out on @fs1 or Bassmaster.com! 

#Bassmaster #BassElite #LakeMurray
Boat #50 to start off day1 of the @bass_nation elite on the new grass covered #santeecooperlakes . This one is going to be a fun one.
I love this stuff. In 17th going into day 2! Hopefully tomorrow we can put something together sooner then waiting till the last min. Let’s make that 50 cut!!!!!
Boat #17 in the @mlfbig5official invitational on #lakeoftheozarks this place is massive. Not really sure what the plan is tomorrow but what i am sure we’ll be throwin at the bank!
Got back on those 20lb sacks! In 2nd going into day 2 of the @mlfbig5official  @tacklewarehouse invitational on #lakeoftheozarks

Got the lead by ounces! Going into the final day of the @mlfbig5official invitational on #lakeoftheozarks @keith_carsonn is a couple spots back. Tune into the Live tomorrow on mlf.com @berkleyfishing @abugarcia_fishing @crestlinerboats @mercurymarine @battlebornbatteries @simmsfishing @tacklewarehouse @planofishing @leupoldoptics @thmarineteam

Last week was like a dream. This week is a different story. Lol  Tomorrow kicks off day 1 of the @bass_nation elites on #laylake I’ll try to get you guys some fish pictures. @berkleyfishing @abugarcia_fishing @crestlinerboats @mercurymarine @battlebornbatteries @tacklewarehouse @planofishing @simmsfishing @leupoldoptics @thmarineteam @lowrancefishing
In 15th going Into day 2 of the @bass_nation elites on #laylake not really sure what the plan is tomorrow except to some how catch 5 keepers and make the 50 cut.
Never been so thrilled to catch 11 pounds! 3 pounds off the top ten cut in 28th place.

The last 5 weeks have been extremely exciting! But having part of the family come at the end of it for the ride back home in the Tundra was priceless! Thank you to everyone that followed each week, my sponsors that make this dream possible and @bass_nation @mlfbig5official for this platform where people that love fishing can chase their dream of moving out of there parents house one day.  @berkleyfishing @abugarcia_fishing @crestlinerboats @mercurymarine @battlebornbatteries @tacklewarehouse @simmsfishing @planofishing @leupoldoptics @thmarineteam @lowrancefishing
In 10th going into day 2 of the @thenationalpfl on #santeecooperlakes

Finished up 9th at the @thenationalpfl on Santee Cooper last week. This week the @bass_nation  elite on the Sabine River. This place is one of the hardest playing fields with changing conditions and obstacles around every corner. Love this place can’t wait to see how it plays out.
In 12th going into day 3 of the @bass_nation elite on the #sabineriver let’s make the top 10 cut!

Boat #40 tomorrow in the @mlfbig5official invitational on the #potomicriver . Last week had a great time hanging out with the family in DC. I can’t wait to set the hook on some tomorrow. Tune into MLF Live tomorrow I might be on there
In 38th place going into day 2 of the @mlfbig5official invitational on the #potomacriver the weights are so tight we need some big ones tomorrow. Also Happy Birthday Dad see u in a few days

Not sure what to chase tomorrow brown or green ones? Saginaw bay @thenationalpfl practice has been a lot of fun got to rescue Nan, Lil, & Melissa from the middle of the bay and also hit some rocks the first 10mins of practice trying to bring @keith_carsonn some Taco Bell. If I didn’t have my @thmarineteam atlas Jack plate all the way up I would be fishing at takeoff this week. I made my mind up the  @crestlinerboats @mercurymarine is going strong let’s run a few hundred miles tomorrow!
Looking at my trolling motor shaft you know what happened.lol Caught over 100 and has us in 23rd place going into day two of the @thenationalpfl #saginawbay going deep tomorrow….. like 7 ft deep
Took the @crestlinerboats #mx21 with @mercurymarine #250proxs for an epic 6hr round trip around #saginawbay for 13 pounds! #worthit 😂 in 28th place going into the final day of the @thenationalpfl
I feel like a new man this morning! Thanks @mercurymarine day1 of practice @bass_nation elite #lakestclair starts today

Almost forgot Happy Birthday LiL! I think that makes about 11 birthdays I’ve missed. Tomorrow kicks off day 1 of the @bass_nation elites on #stclair i’m finding myself knee deep in @berkleyfishing #maxscent

@bass_nation elite on #lakestclair got me pretty good day1 but we got revenge day 2 and held our spot tied for 3rd in the AoY points with @tyler_rivet_trfishing. Had a great time with the the family #miraculousladybug and crew, bill dance aka @patrickrenwick and Breanna Lester @brandonlesterfishing if I wasn’t married you’re sister would be in trouble. 😂

My hair is coming in nice……. Second to last @bass_nation elite starts tomorrow. Got the @crestlinerboats @mercurymarine gassed up and ready to ride the waves on lake Champlain. @berkleyfishing #swamplord will be available soon. I love my @leupoldoptics shades

I try to fish out deep and I turn into @johnhoyerfish The last @bass_nation elite of the season starts tomorrow on the #stlawrenceriver. The smallmouthin has whooped my butt the last two years. I’m ready for a 25lb sack.
#stlawrenceriver is something else! Had 23pounds which puts us in 17th place going into day 2. 🤯
Caught 24 pounds today and slid inside the top ten going into day 3. What a place to have the final @bass_nation of the season. Check the 🐝 out in front of Nan’s head
